value.snippet: fuck you ( plural fuck yous ) ( vulgar) An insulting and humiliating action against somebody. Humiliating your kid on national television for a short-term profit is one of the biggest fuck yous that a parent can ever give to their own child. value.name: Fuck you Definition & Meaning | Dictionary.com
value.snippet: fuck you Also get fucked; go fuck yourself. A curse meaning “go to hell.” For example, Fuck you—go get your own dinner! or Get out of here, get fucked! or, as John Dos Passos had it in 1919 (1931): “Joe got sore and told him to go fuck himself.” The first and third of these vulgar curses date from the late 1800s, and the second from about 1950.
